Testing RAII pattern with exceptions
Test 1: Normal execution with cleanup
Opened file: data.txt
Read: Data from data.txt
Closing file: data.txt
Resource cleaned up successfully
---
Test 2: Exception during operation with cleanup
Opened file: config.json
Read: Data from config.json
Caught exception: Processing error
Closing file: config.json
Resource cleaned up after exception
---
Test 3: Nested scopes with multiple resources
Opened file: outer.txt
Opened file: inner.txt
Reading from both resources
Inner exception: Inner operation failed
Closing file: inner.txt
Outer scope continues
Closing file: outer.txt
All nested resources cleaned up
RAII test completed
